com.noctarius.tengi.spi.serialization.codec

Interface AutoClosableDecoder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Decoder

    public interface AutoClosableDecoder
extends Decoder, AutoCloseable
    The AutoClosableDecoder describes an auto-closable version of a Decoder to be used with try-with-resource constructs.
